<p>AngularJS directives are extended HTML attributes with the prefix ng- 
<p>AngularJS extends HTML with ng-directives.
<p><b>ng-app :</b>The ng-app directive  is used to initialize an AngularJS application.

<p><b>ng-model:</b>The ng-model directive binds the value of HTML controls (input, select, textarea) to application data.

<p><b>ng-bind:</b>The ng-bind directive binds application data to the HTML view.
